snippet.title: [3-ALL Clear] Frog & Spiders [ARCADE] - 36,590 🐸 🕸
snippet.description:
This is Frog and Spiders, Taito 1981, 3-All Clear to 4-2. Such a odd game, and very frustrating as a game can go south in seconds. I played this for the 1st quarter of the MGL Tournament, 2020.


#FrogSpiders #Arcade #Taito
